# Checkbox — React

Package: `@acko/checkbox`
Directive: `"use client"` (interactive)

## Props Interface

```typescript
interface CheckboxProps {
  label?: string;
  description?: string;
  checked: boolean;
  indeterminate?: boolean;
  onChange: (checked: boolean) => void;
  size?: 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg';
  disabled?: boolean;
  error?: boolean;
  className?: string;
}
```

## Key Behaviors

- `indeterminate` is set via ref callback on the native input
- Inline SVG for check (checkmark) and minus (indeterminate) icons — no icon library dependency
- `forwardRef` on the `<label>` wrapper

## Accessibility

- Hidden native checkbox for screen readers
- `aria-invalid` when error
- `aria-describedby` links to description text
- `:focus-visible` on native input targets the custom box

## Exports

```typescript
